&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Collaborate closely and c&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;learly articulate design decisions to a vast set of partners including &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;multidisciplinary creatives on the Brand Studio team and with our internal partners across Marketing and Product&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
