&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Proven leadership in building, mentoring, and motivating senior engineers while maintaining a high technical bar and recruiting top talent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Deeply passionate about the testing, observability, and tooling space, with proven hands-on or leadership experience driving impact in these areas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Demonstrated success delivering scalable, high-quality work and driving cross-functional initiatives in fast-paced, ambiguous environments&lt;/li&gt;
