&lt;li&gt;Monitor team performance and support them in exceeding their goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We’d love to hear from you if you have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience as a frontline manager leading Solutions Consultants or Sales Engineers, with direct accountability for team performance, coaching, and feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of relevant customer-facing technical experience in roles such as Sales Engineering, Solutions Consulting, Engineering, or Sales within a SaaS organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to design and implement strategic programs that drive impact across teams, while also acting as a hands-on problem solver who coaches effectively but can also jump in as a player when needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills with practitioner and executive audiences, including the ability to present complex technical concepts clearly and concisely to both technical and non-technical audiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated success collaborating with cross-functional partners, including Sales, Product, Customer Success, and Support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You embody our values and can thrive in a constantly evolving and growing environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
