job.job_description:
&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Figma is growing our team of passionate creatives and builders on a mission to make design accessible to all. Figma’s platform helps teams bring ideas to life—whether you&#39;re brainstorming, creating a prototype, translating designs into code, or iterating with AI. From idea to product, Figma empowers teams to streamline workflows, move faster, and work together in real time from anywhere in the world. If you&#39;re excited to shape the future of design and collaboration, join us!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re growing our Talent team—and we couldn’t be more excited! We’re looking for an experienced Product Recruiter to help scale our Product organization. You’ll own the full recruiting lifecycle: building pipeline strategy, crafting creative outreach, and closing exceptional talent across IC and leadership levels. You’ll partner closely with Product leaders and the Recruiting team to refine how we hire and build a world-class Product org. If you’re energized by fast-paced, high-impact work—we’d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time role that can be held from one of our US hubs or remotely in the United States.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do at Figma:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead full-cycle recruiting for Product roles, including Product Managers, Product Leaders, and Technical Program Managers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Product leadership to design smart, scalable top-of-funnel strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft thoughtful outreach that sparks interest and reflects Figma’s voice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deeply understand Figma’s products and mission—and share that story with candidates in an authentic way&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the main point of contact for candidates, ensuring a smooth, inclusive, and memorable experience from first hello to final offer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay organized across pipelines and track progress through data and metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously improve our interview process to help us assess talent more effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate across teams to lead and contribute to high-impact recruiting projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We&#39;d love to hear from you if you have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of full-cycle technical recruiting experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years focused on Product or Design recruiting&lt;/li&gt;
