&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with HRIS systems like Workday&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Certified Equity Professional (CEP Level 3)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CPA or equivalent tax background&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
