job.job_description:
&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Figma is growing our team of passionate creatives and builders on a mission to make design accessible to all. Figma’s platform helps teams bring ideas to life—whether you&#39;re brainstorming, creating a prototype, translating designs into code, or iterating with AI. From idea to product, Figma empowers teams to streamline workflows, move faster, and work together in real time from anywhere in the world. If you&#39;re excited to shape the future of design and collaboration, join us!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a talented AI Automation Engineer to join our internal tooling and automation team. This role will focus primarily on designing and deploying AI agents, MCP modules, and agent-to-agent communication frameworks that power the next generation of automation at Figma. The ideal candidate will bring strong expertise in applied AI, agent architectures, and building AI for enterprise/internal use cases, with additional experience in SaaS integrations (MuleSoft or equivalent).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time role that can be held from one of our US hubs or remotely in the United States.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;What you’ll do at Figma:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;179&quot; data-end=&quot;307&quot;&gt;
&lt;div data-start=&quot;181&quot; data-end=&quot;307&quot;&gt;Design, build, and deploy AI agents, MCP modules, and internal tools that automate complex workflows and reduce manual work&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;308&quot; data-end=&quot;429&quot;&gt;
&lt;div data-start=&quot;310&quot; data-end=&quot;429&quot;&gt;Develop multi-agent communication and orchestration frameworks to enable collaboration and autonomous task execution&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;430&quot; data-end=&quot;563&quot;&gt;
&lt;div data-start=&quot;432&quot; data-end=&quot;563&quot;&gt;Partner with Finance, HR, Sales, Engineering, and IT to identify and deliver high-impact opportunities for AI-powered automation&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;564&quot; data-end=&quot;714&quot;&gt;
&lt;div data-start=&quot;566&quot; data-end=&quot;714&quot;&gt;Integrate and optimize enterprise systems (Salesforce, NetSuite, Stripe, Snowflake, etc.) using APIs, data pipelines, and platforms like MuleSoft&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;715&quot; data-end=&quot;863&quot;&gt;
&lt;div data-start=&quot;717&quot; data-end=&quot;863&quot;&gt;Ensure reliability, scalability, compliance, and performance through rigorous testing, debugging, and monitoring of AI systems and integrations&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;864&quot; data-end=&quot;999&quot;&gt;
&lt;div data-start=&quot;866&quot; data-end=&quot;999&quot;&gt;Stay ahead of advancements in LLMs, orchestration frameworks, and AI platforms, applying them pragmatically to Figma’s ecosystem&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1000&quot; data-end=&quot;1132&quot;&gt;
&lt;div data-start=&quot;1002&quot; data-end=&quot;1132&quot;&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally and document architectures, workflows, and communication models for transparency and reusability&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;section page-centered&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;We&#39;d love to hear from you if you have:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;395&quot; data-end=&quot;519&quot;&gt;Proven experience building and deploying AI agents, orchestration frameworks, or LLM-powered applications in production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;520&quot; data-end=&quot;621&quot;&gt;Deep understanding of agent architectures, multi-agent communication, and AI workflow automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;622&quot; data-end=&quot;736&quot;&gt;Hands-on experience with modern AI/ML frameworks and APIs (LangChain, OpenAI, Anthropic, Google Gemini, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;737&quot; data-end=&quot;817&quot;&gt;Strong understanding of API design, RESTful services, and SaaS integrations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;818&quot; data-end=&quot;900&quot;&gt;Experience with MuleSoft or other iPaaS platforms is a plus, but not required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;901&quot; data-end=&quot;985&quot;&gt;Prior experience designing AI for internal enterprise tools is highly desirable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;While not required, it’s an added plus if you also have:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent analytical, problem-solving, and debugging skills&lt;/li&gt;
